# Accounts work

Create table for tracking all stripe balance transactions
Store balance trans id, date created, gross, fee, net, type, event_id, user_id, is_membership
Split into payments, refunds, payouts, bank-related charges
Add button for loading these from stripe

Create table for all BoS transactions with:
date, reference, amount
Add flow for CSV import

Create table for accounting ledger with
date, account_id, bos_or_stripe, amount

Create table for id, account, subaccount, is_closed
Make add account form
Allow closing for say old trip accounts
Accounts for Kit, every trip, membership

Add reconciliation flow

OR - just create a way to map transaction IDs to event / user IDs and event / user names, or to membership - this only requires the first table.


